	* several Makefile.am files: modern linking dependency set
	* config/automake/scripts.am: cross-directory dep-ordered builds
	* amandad-src/amandad.c: block against NULL string-ptr in debug output
	* autogen, buildpkg: run autogen if configure is missing
	* packaging/rpm/amanda.spec.src: add libtool, libxslt, rpcgen as build deps
	* config/amanda/amanda_configure.m4: prefer rpc/rpc.h over libtirpc
	* config/amanda/version.m4: use SO_VERSION var for suffix/SO_NAME of libraries

